{"tid":322251,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇左悟空傳？","createTime":"2017-07-14T16:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T09:08:20.000Z","uid":16055,"like":13,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6eb7222b97cb100b955f29c63bac092ce1001b7","tid":322251,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"剛睇完 其實幾失望 但算係呢幾年最好睇<br />\n<br />\n先從人物開始講<br />\n彭演技正常<br />\n可惜成部電影比人一種佢已經係主角<br />\n唔需要詳細講佢的感覺<br />\n完全比天篷呢對情侶比下去<br />\n二郎神演得好正<br />\n猶其合埋眼打果到<br />\n女主無論人設定演技都係最差<br />\n天篷就演技好但本身個樣就唔適合呢個角色<br />\n<br />\n其次係打鬥<br />\n配樂入得唔好<br />\n孫悟空出場用返周星馳用開果首<br />\n好多打鬥比人感覺抄西遊<br />\n所以係差<br />\n<br />\n最後係電影整體<br />\n其實都差<br />\n一幕幕感人場面好似排隊出場<br />\n完全公式化<br />\n其他拍得到普普通通<br />\n<br />\n如果香港遲d上<br />\n同女或得閒可以去睇果種<br />\n<br />\n利申：大陸買飛睇唔係睇流出無特技版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c10040f345a52e160ac30abca679346a9ec3ed","tid":322251,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:11:43.000Z","msg":"以為你講書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4c5cf03937916ffecf670a45eea45732422e34","tid":322251,"uid":38261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"書有feel好多"},{"pid":"854af0ee48c6afa8b20233fb1ffb40b4d397fe93","tid":322251,"uid":118562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為你講書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以為講書+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a621fe040510362fa8595f49b93a112cf0773726","tid":322251,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"想睇 但聽講劇本寫得唔多掂 有少少卻步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a103ab92dddb6937c3a073933d35628585a6576b","tid":322251,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"