lockquote><br />\n我咁岩有飛去ua睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bb20ce564477803cdc22d1aaf6bd0da74245e4","tid":322251,"uid":123936,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"好睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好動漫feel，同好型。因為我比較鐘意衣類型，類似火影，海賊王咁，加埋啲老套劇情變超級撒亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。重點都係熱血動漫既老土劇情「堅持某一種信念就成功既既劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」所以係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以一個低成本同一個香港導彈拍出咁既片係比較少見。係一開頭比較亂，狂打唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落左凡間先好睇番。我覺得10分有8分"},{"pid":"0d5ba228b1cf578484ec77ea57739c33876b93ec","tid":322251,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"本書比套鳩野累撚死"},{"pid":"1f91249ab3f7130dde1fb1497c338da630c983af","tid":322251,"uid":97114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇香港影評人話好睇<br />\n仲想話想香港快上<br />\non9<br />\n豆瓣評分仲差過西遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩求其睇左啲影評<br />\n好似好多個影評人都以為係西遊記改篇<br />\n唔知有悟空傳呢本原著<br />\n可能因為咁無乜期待就有驚喜掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得原著講既限界真係好乎合我地既人生 仲有好多有味道既情節 電影完全出唔到種意境"},{"pid":"acba873821a9425060e89225560649843c15518a","tid":322251,"uid":75143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾黎<br />\n今日入左場睇<br />\n奉勸各位巴絲可以慳返唔好入場<br />\n睇annabelle好過<br />\n<br />\n配樂認同入得好差 <br />\n劇情又劣<br />\n天蓬條感