 />\n但依套係近年好打動到我既電影</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得ua多d場次，又有國粤兩版揀<br />\n好多戲院都係得d西時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有兩個港台一線男星+西遊記商業大片，仲要郭子健係香港都算有質素既導演</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上個月睇「明月幾時有」仲少場次呀，除咗3個男女主角唔係香港人(但都係大卡士), 其他演員大部份香港人，仲要係許鞍華導演。故仔講香港嘅故事，根本算係香港電影。"},{"pid":"ada75f0b4a8e7d1185878741eb07883803970fe4","tid":322251,"uid":45505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"想知同小說有咩唔同"},{"pid":"d7fa011efaf786421e681a1eca080560af87b52d","tid":322251,"uid":100453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"想知邊到有途徑睇小說<br />\n有冇實體書買"},{"pid":"0ef410f476a7b108cf1143327e0871648046a066","tid":322251,"uid":35166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/66rWWyN94qA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F66rWWyN94qA&d=5Cz7%2FRjhriApYT0U1Dyvv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=47280b6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/66rWWyN94qA</a><br />\n<br />\n值得一睇既訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完郭子健所講既野，好多人疑惑既事，都有入面解釋<br />\n<br />\n對套戲更了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}